  <tr>
   <td colspan="4" class="content">
    <pre>It appears that Django's bite-sized bugs changed internally from using a keyword ("easy-pickings") 
to using a field in Trac:

<a href="https://code.djangoproject.com/query?">https://code.djangoproject.com/query?</a>
status=assigned&amp;status=new&amp;easy=1&amp;col=id&amp;col=summary&amp;col=status&amp;col=owner&amp;col=type&amp;col
=component&amp;order=priority

This is not represented in the OpenHatch interface.</pre>
   </td>
  </tr>
 
